data.description: Nicely updated home on corner lot with fenced yard. This home features three bedrooms and laundry on the main floor. Primary bedroom has walk in closet and 3/4 bath with great tiled shower. Main floor also offers a full bathroom, large living room, dining/kitchen area with walk out doors to back yard. Kitchen has abundant cupboard space, and is open to dining/living area, which makes this a perfect home for entertaining. Lower level has two additional bedrooms, great storage areas, and a rough in area for the addition of a third bathroom. All your fixtures are there, just install as you'd like in your new bathroom. Two car attached garage offers extra space for your mower or toys. This is a great space to call home!
